OL,3,CRoadworkers receive stab threats with
OL,4,Cone run over in spate of abuse
OL,6,FRoadworkers in a Berkshire town say
OL,7,Fthey have received stab threats during
OL,8,Fa spate of repeated abuse by members
OL,9,Fof the public.
OL,11,FOne worker was run over deliberately
OL,12,Fwhile working at California Crossroads
OL,13,Fin Finchampstead.
OL,15,FIt has become so bad that Wokingham
OL,16,FBorough Council is pleading for a
OL,17,Fchange in behaviour with workers now
OL,18,Fbeing supplied with body worn cameras
OL,19,Ffor their protection from the abuse.
