OL,6,F"On Tuesday a motorist threatened to
OL,7,Fstab a worker before speeding off
OL,8,Fwhile the crew were setting up traffic
OL,9,Fcontrols to close Nine Mile Ride.
OL,10,FLater, another motorist threatened to
OL,11,Fpunch a worker.
OL,13,F"A physical assault took place
OL,14,Fyesterday/on Wednesday morning when a
OL,15,Fdriver intentionally hit a road worker
OL,16,Fusing their vehicle, before fleeing
OL,17,Fthe scene. The car's registration
OL,18,Fnumber has been submitted to police
OL,19,Ffor investigation.
