OL,6,F"The workers are equipped with body
OL,7,Fcameras to capture any incidents and
OL,8,Fsupply to police for prosecution.
OL,10,F"Works at California Cross, which
OL,11,Fstarted this week, are designed to
OL,12,Fbring a sense of community to the
OL,13,Fcentre of Finchampstead village by
OL,14,Fimproving the area for pedestrians,
OL,15,Fredesigning access to the car parking
OL,16,Fareas, and installing attractive new
OL,17,Fstreetlights, plantings, bollards and
OL,18,Ftotems."
